131
00:06:31,980 --> 00:06:35,170
So now we know that of the five missing booksellers,

132
00:06:35,170 --> 00:06:37,950
one is clearly helping with an investigation,

133
00:06:37,950 --> 00:06:41,290
and the other is clearly a very bad man.

134
00:06:41,290 --> 00:06:42,530
So in conclusion...

135
00:06:42,530 --> 00:06:45,610
we should just stop asking questions about
the other three.

136
00:06:45,610 --> 00:06:47,080
Because at the end of the day,

137
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:50,530
China honors its commitment to one country,
two systems.

138
